A little Dior moment 🎀❤️ Look at the Addict lip glow, it is almost empty. I love this lip balm, it leaves a beautiful pink tint and so moisturizing! Next fave is the lip glow oil what I also use as lip mask. My well loved Backstage Rose Glow blush has seen better days too.🤭 Lip Maximizer in Holo Pink is such a versatile lip gloss with a beautiful shimmery finish. Lastly the Miss Dior Body Milk has a rich milky texture I started to use it again now that the weather got cooler.
